following the rules.

17
00:00:40,083 --> 00:00:42,250
Sharpen the weapon
in your heart!

18
00:00:42,333 --> 00:00:44,791
Make reality bow
down to your will!

19
00:00:44,875 --> 00:00:48,125
Just do that, and the
future will be all yours.

20
00:02:18,625 --> 00:02:22,750
I'm the chairperson of
Hiiragi Academy, Koyomi Hiiragi.

21
00:02:22,833 --> 00:02:25,291
And I am here
today to recruit you.

22
00:02:25,375 --> 00:02:28,833
Mr. Junichiro Kagami.

23
00:02:28,916 --> 00:02:30,666
What, like, for the horde?

24
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:31,833
Pardon?

25
