your mind right now.

34
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:56,250
I can see it on your face,
as plain as day.

35
00:02:56,333 --> 00:02:57,541
[gasps]

36
00:02:57,625 --> 00:02:59,916
"A sexy girl like her
surely has options,

37
