chairperson of a school?"

38
00:03:02,666 --> 00:03:04,833
[JUNICHIRO]
That's not what I'm thinking!

39
00:03:04,916 --> 00:03:06,666
And while I am
loaded with options,

40
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:09,375
