Academy chairperson.

42
00:03:12,125 --> 00:03:13,708
[JUNICHIRO]
What's with the options?

43
00:03:13,791 --> 00:03:16,916
If you've got so much going on,
then why come and find me?

44
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,833
