to find elite teachers

45
00:03:18,916 --> 00:03:20,416
who are looking for
work these days.

46
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:21,916
[sighs]
My only claim to fame

47
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,625
is that article I
wrote five years ago.

48
00:03:23,708 --> 00:03:25,125
