much higher than that.

52
00:03:33,791 --> 00:03:37,666
Mr. Kagami. My goal
is to change Japan.

53
00:03:37,750 --> 00:03:40,458
We as a people must
continue to prosper.

54
00:03:40,541 --> 00:03:42,291
So, My school promotes

55
00:03:42,375 --> 00:03:44,666
forward-thinking
through education.

56
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:47,625
Our students develop values
based on neither economics,

57
00:03:47,708 --> 00:03:49,791
nor standard industry capital.

58
00:03:51,083 --> 00:03:53,541
[KOYOMI] My vision
is simple, yet profound.

59
00:03:53,625 --> 00:03:56,708
Amusing Country, Japan!

60
00:03:56,791 --> 00:03:58,041
In order to achieve this,

61
00:03:58,125 --> 00:04:01,125
