such as yourself.

62
00:04:01,208 --> 00:04:04,291
So I implore you, please
consider my generous offer.

63
00:04:04,375 --> 00:04:07,833
This country needs you
and your eccentricities.

64
00:04:07,916 --> 00:04:09,541
