mansion than a school.

90
00:05:24,041 --> 00:05:25,375
[SUZUNE]
They get great teachers, too,

91
00:05:25,458 --> 00:05:27,125
but the students
are so hardcore,

92
00:05:27,208 --> 00:05:28,708
