a maid café. Just great.

499
00:23:42,208 --> 00:23:45,375
So, uh. Moe, moe.

500
00:23:45,458 --> 00:23:47,666
This is stupid,
I'm not saying it!

501
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:50,083
Period Four,
"Dignity of Maids."

502
00:23:50,166 --> 00:23:52,708
What the heck does "maid
among maids" even mean?

503
00:23:52,791 --> 00:23:54,375
[MAKINA gasps]
Wait a minute.

504
00:23:54,458 --> 00:23:56,541
Who is this "Razor Girl,"
anyway?

